\lim_{x\rightarrow 0} \frac{\sqrt{2+x}-\sqrt{2}}{x}=\lim_{x\rightarrow 0} \frac{1}{\sqrt{x+2}+\sqrt{2}}=\frac{\sqrt{2}}{4}.
